into that black box from now on.

740
00:53:33,079 --> 00:53:35,100
You have to share that video with us.

741
00:53:36,228 --> 00:53:37,200
Yeah.

742
00:53:42,183 --> 00:53:45,203
If I'd just thought of that black box
when I first saw the CCTV...

743
00:53:45,671 --> 00:53:47,276
it wouldn't have taken this long.

744
00:53:48,990 --> 00:53:50,713
Why am I so stupid?

745
00:53:52,323 --> 00:53:53,677
I'm really sorry.

746
00:53:59,693 --> 00:54:02,175
Stop saying you're sorry.
What are you so sorry about?

747
00:54:03,224 --> 00:54:06,142
-I was just...
-You didn't slander my father.

748
00:54:06,533 --> 00:54:09,875
You didn't frame Chan-soo.
So why do you keep apologizing?

749
00:54:10,713 --> 00:54:11,926
You're being strange.

750
00:54:12,503 --> 00:54:14,241
Why do you keep getting mad at me?

751
00:54:14,332 --> 00:54:16,719
You're making me mad and irritating me.

752
00:54:18,513 --> 00:54:19,953
You said it before.

753
00:54:20,053 --> 00:54:22,513
You told me not to worry about you,
or to comfort you.

754
00:54:22,613 --> 00:54:24,691
You told me to stay still
so that you won't fall apart.

755
00:54:25,483 --> 00:54:27,857
All that I can do is to be sorry.
So what do you want me to do then?

756
00:54:29,363 --> 00:54:30,596
That bugs me too.

757
00:54:34,093 --> 00:54:35,172
Fine.

758
00:54:36,103 --> 00:54:37,840
I really won't do anything from now on.

759
00:54:38,463 --> 00:54:40,533
From now on, I won't
worry or comfort you.

760
00:54:41,372 --> 00:54:42,414
Or even feel sorry toward you.

761
00:54:43,413 --> 00:54:44,521
Is that enough?

762
00:56:14,160 --> 00:56:18,962
I was thinking that it's too shameless
to eat four bowls and just leave.

763
00:56:51,392 --> 00:56:52,938
Don't feel sorry.

764
00:56:55,013 --> 00:56:58,601
You're neither Song Cha-ok's daughter
nor a niece to me.

765
00:56:59,983 --> 00:57:01,461
To me, you're just you.

766
00:57:02,943 --> 00:57:05,269
Dal-Po. I mean Ha-myung.

767
00:57:06,673 --> 00:57:08,175
You can call me Dal-Po.

768
00:57:11,933 --> 00:57:16,184
I tried so hard. I tried everything.

769
00:57:18,263 --> 00:57:19,757
But it's been the same way
for a long time.

770
00:57:21,613 --> 00:57:25,763
When I think about my father,
my brother, and your mother,

771
00:57:25,863 --> 00:57:27,863
I know that I shouldn't be doing this.

772
00:57:29,823 --> 00:57:30,939
But I can't give you up.

773
00:57:33,063 --> 00:57:34,022
So we...

774
00:57:39,143 --> 00:57:40,644
I'm the same as you.

775
00:58:01,253 --> 00:58:02,561
Do you want to stop by my house?

776
00:58:03,083 --> 00:58:05,947
-Your house? What house?
-The house I'm living in now.

777
00:58:06,433 --> 00:58:09,473
Son! It's natural for you to come home.
How did we become like this?

778
00:58:09,573 --> 00:58:12,043
-The ones behind the fire...
-What do you want to say?

779
00:58:12,143 --> 00:58:14,993
-Mother!
-It seems we need to be more careful now.

780
00:58:15,093 --> 00:58:17,283
The earlier ones
were intentionally deleted?

781
00:58:17,383 --> 00:58:21,916
Choi In-ha.
How can you sleep in this situation?
